  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2419970/extras/ba3d3df0495b3ea379f3bb02e61c3aa2.poster.avif?t=1743857250\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2419970/extras/ba3d3df0495b3ea379f3bb02e61c3aa2.webm?t=1743857250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2419970/extras/ba3d3df0495b3ea379f3bb02e61c3aa2.mp4?t=1743857250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><u><i><strong></strong></i></u>Pigeon Flight Simulator is designed for those who want to take a break from the fast-paced city life and enjoy a relaxing flight experience. Glide between skyscrapers, soar over parks and rivers, and find peace with soothing music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is developed to let you enjoy flying without any tasks or competitive pressure. With a realistic physics engine and immersive visuals, <strong>Relaxing Fly Mode</strong> helps you unwind, connecting you with the serene harmony of the city and nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A calm flight experience can help balance your mood and reduce stress. Take a break from the rush of daily life, spread your wings, and enjoy the freedom!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2419970/extras/ba3d3df0495b3ea379f3bb02e61c3aa2.poster.avif?t=1743857250\" width=600 height=244 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2419970/extras/ba3d3df0495b3ea379f3bb02e61c3aa2.webm?t=1743857250\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2419970/extras/ba3d3df0495b3ea379f3bb02e61c3aa2.mp4?t=1743857250\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><u><i><strong></strong></i></u>Pigeon Flight Simulator is designed for those who want to take a break from the fast-paced city life and enjoy a relaxing flight experience. Glide between skyscrapers, soar over parks and rivers, and find peace with soothing music.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is developed to let you enjoy flying without any tasks or competitive pressure. With a realistic physics engine and immersive visuals, <strong>Relaxing Fly Mode</strong> helps you unwind, connecting you with the serene harmony of the city and nature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A calm flight experience can help balance your mood and reduce stress. Take a break from the rush of daily life, spread your wings, and enjoy the freedom!</p>",
